C%20and%20that%20was%20coming%20off%20several%20prior%20years%20of%20underwhelming%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Five%20Below%20was%20managing%20to%20grow%20overall%20sales%20through%20the%20addition%20of%20new%20stores%2C%20existing%20stores%20weren't%20resonating%20with%20shoppers.%20It%20was%20also%20dealing%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-below-reduces-self-checkout-service-checks-receipts-theft-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindustry-wide%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20shoplifting%C2%A0and%20the%20rise%20of%20low-priced%20e-commerce%20players%20like%20Shein%20and%20Temu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Five%20Below's%20stock%20languishing%20around%20a%20third%20of%20its%202023%20peak%2C%20the%20company%20tapped%20Park%2C%20then-CEO%20of%20Forever%2021%2C%20to%20take%20over%20as%20CEO%20in%20December%202024%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-tree-five-below-holiday-decorations-comparison-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eholiday%20rush%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272d9e53e-5097-4c6d-b49d-e98844de4629%5C%22%3EBetting%20on%20Park's%20'complete%20package'%20of%20retail%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20came%20in%2C%20she%20was%20sort%20of%20an%20unknown%20quantity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mizuho%20retail%20analyst%20David%20Bellinger%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20question%20of%20how%20is%20she%20going%20to%20fix%20this%20business%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Park%20may%20not%20have%20been%20the%20most%20widely%20known%20CEO%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20she%20did%20come%20equipped%20with%20decades%20of%20industry%20experience%2C%20including%20as%20CEO%20of%20Forever%2021%20and%20Paper%20Source%2C%20as%20well%20as%20executive%20roles%20at%20Duty%20Free%20Shoppers%20and%20Levi's%2C%20and%20a%20stint%20with%20McKinsey's%20retail%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20backg