uot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20merchandising%20effort%20was%20also%20paired%20with%20a%20social%20media%20push%20that%20the%20company%20says%20has%20helped%20attract%20new%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPark's%20other%20major%20area%20of%20focus%20was%20simplifying%20store%20operations%20for%20both%20employees%20and%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20bit%20of%20planning%20and%20an%20incremental%20investment%20in%20labor%20hours%2C%20Five%20Below%20says%20it%20has%20improved%20in-stock%20rates%20and%20customer%20support%20at%20its%20stores%2C%20helping%20to%20drive%20higher%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWinnie%20Park%20is%20the%20type%20of%20leader%20that%20has%20a%20very%20clear%20vision%20for%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Saunders%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20doesn't%20really%20overcomplicate%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202ff4863-be64-4ab1-ac48-ea2110a641a0%5C%22%3ELetting%20some%20things%20go%20can%20help%20the%20business%20move%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20getting%20Five%20Below%20back%20to%20some%20principles%20it%20may%20have%20lost%20touch%20with%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20Park%20is%20also%20showing%20a%20willingness%20to%20let%20go%20of%20at%20least%20one%20thing%20that%20may%20have%20been%20holding%20the%20company%20back%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-below-photo-tour-shows-how-fitness-and-beauty-merchandise-made-it-successful-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eits%20%245%20price%20point%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20years%20of%20inflation%20haven't%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20retailers%20with%20dollar-denominated%20branding%20to%20stick%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-tree-raises-some-prices-1-50-stickers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20original%20promises%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dollar%20Tree%20had%20to%20hike%20its%20base%20price%20to%20%241.25%2C%20and%20it's%20tough%20to%20run%20a%2099%20Cents%20Only%20store%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20US%20government%20is%20eliminating%20the%20penny.%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20this%20year%20hasn't%20been%20much%20help%20for%20import-heavy%20businesses%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20manage%20these%20cost%20pressures%2C%20the%20company%20lumped%20more%20merchandise%20in%20a%20catch-all%20section%20of%20the%20store%20called%20Five%20Beyond%2C%20which%20it%20had%20set%20up%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20distinction%20brought%20unnecessary%20complexity%20without%20meaningful%20benefit%2C%20and%20the%20company%20recently%20ditched%20the%20plan%20in%20favor%20of%20grouping%20products%20by%20category%20instead%20of%20a%20price%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20disjointed%20merchandising%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20Bellinger%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20in%20that%20price%20threshold%20was%20in%20the%20back%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20way%20they've%20assorted%20the%20store%20and%20spread%20these%20items%20out%20makes%20a%20lot%20more%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb2a02fb-b078-4c95-b02c-99272e9f1d59%5C%22%3ELooking%20beyond%20price%20to%20focus%20on%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBellinger%20said%20the%20move%20shows%20that%20Park%20understands%20a%20critical%20lesson%20that%20successful%20retailers%20have%20had%20to%20reckon%20with%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%3A%20value%20and%20price%20are%20not%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20find%20value%20in%20that%20%2430%20item.%20It's%20all%20relative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaken%20together%20%E2%80%94%20exciting%20products%2C%20well-run%20stores%2C%20a%20focus%20on%20great%20value%20%E2%80%94%20Five%20Below%20is%20starting%20to%20look%20in%20some%20ways%20more%20like%20a%20warehouse%20club%20than%20a%20discount%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFive%20Below%20is%20essentially%20the%20Costco%20for%20kids