20told%20investors%20it%20was%20closing%20down%20due%20to%20the%20high%20costs%20of%20talent%20in%20September.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm%20had%20more%20than%20250%20people%20based%20in%20nine%20offices%20across%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20manager%20has%20had%20discussions%20with%20onetime%20rival%20funds%20about%20purchasing%20their%20risk%20system%2C%20Photon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShutting%20down%20a%20hedge%20fund%20isn't%20as%20simple%20as%20turning%20off%20the%20lights%20and%20handing%20the%20office%20keys%20to%20the%20building%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrades%20need%20to%20be%20wound%20down%20slowly%20to%20make%20sure%20backers%20don't%20lose%20money%20in%20a%20fire%20sale.%20Employment%20contracts%20with%20payouts%20and%20deferred%20compensation%20need%20to%20be%20honored.%20Anything%20worth%20selling%20needs%20to%20find%20a%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%243.2%20billion%20Eisler%20Capital%2C%20the%20London-based%20multistrategy%20fund%20founded%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%20veteran%20Ed%20Eisler%2C%20the%20firm's%20late%20September%20letter%20to%20investors%20about%20liquidating%20the%20firm%20was%20just%20the%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ed%20Eisler%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693c52bd64858d02d216b980%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEd%20Eisler%2C%20founder%20of%20Eisler%20Capital%3Cp%3EDavid%20M.%20Benett%2FDave%20Benett%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Mulberry%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20had%20transformed%20itself%20from%20a%20macro%20shop%20into%20a%20fund%20with%20dozens%20of%20different%20teams%20trading%20their%20own%20specialities%20and%20had%20ambitious%20goals.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20Business%20Insider%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-multi-strategy-firms-are-balancing-growth-investor-demand-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20end%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Eisler's%20COO%2C%20Chris%20Milner%2C%20said%20the%20manager%20had%20increased%20head%20count%20by%20more%20than%2040%25%20that%20year%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20our%20capital%20partners%20and%20the%20Street%20right%20now%20and%20don't%20feel%20constrained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20is%20grow%20for%20growth's%20sake.%20Against%20that%2C%20though%2C%20we%20are%20an%20ambitious%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20Milner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%202023%20was%20a%20high%20point%20for%20the%20firm.%20The%20firm%20made%203%25%20in%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-hedge-funds-returns-performance-schonfeld-citadel-millennium-deshaw-walleye-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrailing%20its%20larger%20multistrategy%20peers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20costs%20mounted.%20Key%20moneymakers%20Adrien%20Delattre%20and%20Lewis%20Morton%20left%20the%20firm%20despite%20being%20named%20partners%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20of%20attracting%20and%20retaining%20experienced%20money%20managers%20capable%20of%20deploying%20capital%20at%20scale%20within%20a%20cost%20structure%20acceptable%20to%20investors%20has%20grown%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20told%20investors%20in%20its%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20typical%20fund%20liquidation%2C%20Eisler%20has%20the%20ongoing%20attention%20of%20the%20industry%20due%20to%20its%20high%20head%20count%20and%20a%20possible%20sale%20of%20some%20of%20the%20firm's%20intellectual%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20talking%20with%20backers%20of%20the%20firm%2C%20people%20close%20to%20the%20manager%2C%20and%20industry%20experts%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20pulled%20together%20the%20latest%20on%20the%20firm's%20potential%20sale%20of%20its%20risk%20system%2C%20Photon%2C%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20rival%20funds%20are%20trying%20to%20hire%2C%20and%20where%20some%20of%20the%20fund's%20investing%20talent%20has%20already%20landed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223aa5880d-ae83-4ac8-9f54-a4ca9020e99e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20battle%20for%20Eisler's%20risk%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Eisler's%20returns%20lagged%20behind%20those%20of%20its%20peers%20in%202025%2C%20with%20a%20loss%20of%201.7%25%20through%20August%2C%20the%20firm's%20risk%20and%20analytics%20system%2C%20developed%20by%20Eisler%20and%20his%20right-hand%20man%2C%20Sam%20Wisnia%2C%20was%20known%20throughout%20the%20industry%20as%20well-designed.%20One%20person%20at%20a%20rival%20fund%20said%20Eisler's%20macro%20background%20gave%20the%20system%20a%20unique%20feel%20compared%20to%20others%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20which%20were%20made%20with%20long-short%20equity%20or%20quant%20trading%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultistrategy%20funds%2C%20the%20sprawling%20giants%20that%20have%20come%20to%20define%20this%20era%20of%20the%20industry%2C%20are%20hyper-focused%20on%20risk%2C%20given%20the%20key%20part%20of%20their%20pitch%20to%20large%20institutional%20investors%3A%20We%20can%20make%20money%20in%20any%20market%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20cutthroat%2C%20immediate%20firings%20for%20any%20PM%20who%20loses%203%25%20are%20not%20as%20common%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-pay-poaching-relocation-mercenaries-buy-loyalty-millennium-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20talent%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20firms%20use%20a%20host%20of%20systems%20and%20tools%20to%20monitor%20the%20exposures%20and%20risks%20of%20each%20trading%20team%2C%20ensuring%20that%20no%20one%20portfolio%20drags%20down%20the%20entire%20fund.%20Eisler's%20Photon%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20for%20tracking%20macro%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20people%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20had%20conversations%20with%20funds%20such%20as%20Verition%20and%20Taula%20Capital%20about%20buying%20the%20system%2C%20which%20is%20named%20Photon.%20Verition%20and%20Taula%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20LPs%20of%20the%20fund%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20are%20frustrated%20that%20the%20money%20made%20from%20the%20potential%20sale%20of%20the%20system%20will%20not%20be%20distributed%20to%20them%2C%20but%20instead%20will%20go%20to%20Eisler%20and%20Wisnia.%20These%20backers%20feel%20entitled%20to%20a%20share%20of%20the%20proceeds%20from%20any%20sale%2C%20given%20that%20their%20pass-through%20fees%20covered%20the%20development%20of%20Photon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20close%20to%20the%20firm%20said%20that%20Eisler's%20legal%20documents%20with%20investors%20clearly%20give%20the%20ownership%20of%20intellectual%20property%2C%20such%20as%20Photon%2C%20to%20the%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed30f2a4-8386-4023-af9c-8540e3214712%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20PM%20everyone%20is%20circling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202023%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20keep%20top%20talent%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20Eisler%20named%20four%20new%20partners.%20A%20little%20over%20a%20year%20later%2C%20three%20of%20them%2C%20including%20the%20aforementioned%20Delattre%20and%20Morton%2C%20had%20departed%20the%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20sign%20for%20how%20top%20performers%20viewed%20the%20manager's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20new%20partner%20who%20stayed%20with%20the%20firm%20through%20its%20closing%20is%20now%20one%20of%20the%20most%20coveted%20potential%20hires%20for%20rivals%2C%20according%20to%20business%20development%20executives%20at%20two%20different%20multistrategy%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassimiliano%20Pignatelli%20is%20a%20Milan-based%20portfolio%20manager%20who%20joined%20Eisler%20in%202020%20after%20a%20stint%20on%20a%20trading%20desk%20for%20Macquarie%20in%20