d%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Harry%20Met%20Sally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Reiner%2C%20the%20award-winning%20director%20of%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Harry%20Met%20Sally%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Princess%20Bride%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Michele%20Singer%20Reiner%2C%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Los%20Angeles%20Police%20Department%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20at%203%3A38%20p.m.%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20department%20received%20a%20medical%20aid%20call%20to%20the%20200%20Block%20of%20Chadbourne%20Avenue%20in%20Brentwood%2C%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20LAPD%20determined%20the%20deaths%20of%20a%2078-year-old%20man%20and%2068-year-old%20woman.%20The%20LAPD%20said%20in%20an%20X%20statement%20that%20its%20Robbery%20Homicide%20Division%20was%20investigating%20an%20apparent%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Sunday%20night%20statement%2C%20LA%20Mayor%20Karen%20Bass%20confirmed%20the%20Reiners'%20deaths%20and%20said%20that%20the%20investigation%20was%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELAPD%20Deputy%20Chief%20Alan%20Hamilton%20said%20in%20a%20Sunday%20night%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20department%20was%20not%20seeking%20anyone%20as%20a%20suspect%20or%20person%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20that%20the%20LAPD%20would%20speak%20with%20the%20couple's%20family%20members%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20family%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20House%20Speaker%20and%20California%20Rep.%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20news%20was%20%26quot%3Bdevastating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20anyone%20more%20remarkable%20and%20excellent%20in%20every%20field%20and%20endeavor%20they%20pursued%2C%26quot%3B%20Pelosi%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BRob%20was%20creative%2C%20funny%2C%20and%20beloved.%20And%20in%20all%20of%20their%20endeavors%2C%20Michelle%20was%20his%20indispensable%20partner%2C%20intellectual%20resource%2C%20and%20loving%20wife.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMichelle%20and%20I%20are%20heartbroken%20by%20the%20tragic%20passing%20of%20Rob%20Reiner%20and%20his%20beloved%20wife%2C%20Michele.%20Rob%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20film%20and%20television%20gave%20us%20some%20of%20our%20most%20cherished%20stories%20on%20screen.%20But%20beneath%20all%20of%20the%20stories%20he%20produced%20was%20a%20deep%20belief%20in%20the%20goodness%20of%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Barack%20Obama%20(%40BarackObama)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBarackObama%2Fstatus%2F2000442913885712602%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EReiner%20had%20a%20long%20and%20illustrious%20career%20in%20Hollywood.%20The%20son%20of%20actor%2C%20director%2C%20and%20screenwriter%20Carl%20Reiner%2C%20he%20studied%20at%20the%20UCLA%20Film%20School%20before%20starting%20his%20directing%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20directed%20several%20iconic%20Hollywood%20movies%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Spinal%20Tap%26quot%3B%20in%201984%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Princess%20Bride%26quot%3B%20in%201987%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Harry%20Met%20Sally%26quot%3B%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReiner%20also%20appeared%20in%20several%20acting%20stints%2C%20including%20movies%20such%20as%20the%202013%20Martin%20Scorsese%20blockbuster%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wolf%20of%20Wall%20Street%26quot%3B%20and%20TV%20series%20%26quot%3BNew%20Girl%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201987%2C%20he%20founded%20Castle%20Rock%20Entertainment%2C%20a%20production%20company%2C%20alongside%20a%20group%20of%20film%20producers.%20The%20company%20is%20now%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReiner%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20three%20children%20together%3A%20Nick%2C%20Jake%2C%20and%20Romy%20Reiner.%20He%20has%20one%20daughter%2C%20Tracy%20Reiner%2C%20from%20his%20previous%20marriage%20to%20actor%20Penny%20Marshall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Reiner%20battled%20drug%20abuse%20in%20his%20teens%20and%20early%20adulthood.%20His%20experience%2C%20including%20stints%20in%20rehab%2C%20led%20him%20to%20write%20the%20screenplay%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frob-reiner-and-nick-reiner-on-drug-abuse-being-charlie-2016-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBeing%20Charlie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%202015%20romance-drama%20that%20his%20father%20directed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Reiner%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20son%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bheart%20and%20soul%20of%20the%20film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frob-reiner-director-princess-bride-dead-78-los-angeles-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765777097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693f888e832e0ef1ead6334d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frob-reiner-director-princess-bride-dead-78-los-angeles-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reiner%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Michelle%20Singer%20Reiner%2C%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20in%20Brentwood%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frob-reiner-director-princess-bride-dead-78-los-